WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:05.255
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:06.056 --> 00:09.059
Well, I'm out of here, I guess.

00:09.059 --> 00:11.561
Going to stop over at the health club.

00:13.563 --> 00:15.065
You belong to a health club?

00:15.065 --> 00:17.567
Yeah, yeah. Vera gave me a
membership for my birthday.

00:17.567 --> 00:20.937
It's, uh, real subtle, huh?

00:20.937 --> 00:22.188
You-You actually go there and work out?

00:22.188 --> 00:25.692
Yeah. I try to do, uh, about
25 in the pool every day.

00:25.692 --> 00:26.609
Laps?

00:26.609 --> 00:28.111
Cannonballs.

00:30.580 --> 00:34.534
(piano plays)

00:34.918 --> 00:36.920
? Making your way in the world today ?

00:36.920 --> 00:39.923
? Takes everything you've got ?

00:39.923 --> 00:42.926
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

00:42.926 --> 00:46.429
? Sure would help a lot ?

00:46.429 --> 00:52.218
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

00:52.218 --> 00:54.220
? Sometimes you want to go ?

00:54.220 --> 00:59.726
? Where everybody knows your name ?

00:59.726 --> 01:04.230
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:04.230 --> 01:06.733
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:06.733 --> 01:09.235
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:09.235 --> 01:14.741
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:14.741 --> 01:17.243
? You want to go where people know ?

01:17.243 --> 01:19.746
? People are all the same ?

